body_html:
I tried using both -DSELECTIVE_REGISTRATION and -DSUPPORT_SELECTIVE_REGISTRATION and removing edits in android_extended_ops_group1 ("cwise_op_asin.cc") and it builds but I get the following on Android:

java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: No OpKernel was registered to support Op 'Asin' with these attrs

This goes away when I add cwise_op_asin.cc to android_extended_ops_group1.
